title: Metal Mulisha Maidens 2014 Fall Collection
description: The Metal Mulisha team set its course to Ocotillo Wells to kick off the 2014 Maidens Fall catalog photo shoot! Besides from putting in a group ride, flipping natural terrain and roosting dirt we turned things up with a Mulisha desert party. Things got a little wild!
